I"o<h4 id="官网"><a href="https://cocoapods.org/">官网</a></h4>
<ul>
  <li>Swift 和 Objective-C Cocoa 项目的包管理工具</li>
  <li>iOS 开发的必备工具</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="安装">安装</h4>
<ol>
  <li>CocoaPods 是用 Ruby 构建的,可以用 macOS 上的默认 Ruby 进行安装</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install cocoapods</code></li>
</ol>

<p>⚠️ ERROR: While executing gem … (Gem::FilePermissionError).
	You don’t have write permissions for the /usr/bin directory.
	- <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install -n /usr/local/bin fastlane</code>
	- <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install -n /usr/local/bin cocoapods</code></p>

<h4 id="使用">使用</h4>
<ul>
  <li>```
pod spec create Peanut</li>
</ul>

<p>pod spec lint Peanut.podspec</p>

<p>```</p>
